n Fu and created in partnership with social media platform TikTok. The video is centered around Lipa and DaBaby dancing in an art deco-styled elevator, with many TikTok users in the cast. Lipa promoted the single with live performances on the Graham Norton Show, at the American Music Awards of 2020, and on Saturday Night Live.	f
