ow known to be “Beta Male Strategies.”\n\nThe album’s track listing and cover art were revealed when the record was put up for pre-order on September 6th, 2019, seven days before its release.\n\nOn September 8th, 2019, JPEGMAFIA released a video of him previewing the record James Blake, who was previously shown in the album’s teaser video, continuing showing previews of “Beta Male Strategies.”	f
